{
  "stem": "10353.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there they organized themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they cooked themselves a goulash there, with cabbage soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was the first time that they gave us some food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Early in the morning, the following morning, they got up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we went with them for a little while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then they said they are turning off this road, and if we want to go to Prague, we have to go straight.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we started to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came into Saturday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Around Saturday noon, we came into a rather populated place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was-- although I spoke German reasonably well, I was afraid to speak German because, you know, the atmosphere was very anti-German at that time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I tried to-- I saw this man in uniform, very beautiful uniform, and I tried to talk to him and tried to talk to him in Hungarian and English, Romanian.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't know any of the languages, 'til finally I told him, maybe in German, a little-- I forgot that I was in Sudetenland, which was-- had a great German population.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why didn't you speak German, he says.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we told him that we come from Theresienstadt-- Terezin, there we call it Terezin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when he heard the word Terezin, he says, you are coming from Terezin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, you come with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took us to a place [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that was a Blue Cross place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they heard that we came from Terezin, they took us around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- what can they do for us?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave us clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave us food.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
